      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TWILIGHT STORM (2) produced a good resuming effort from the back row when 3.5 metres away in second after working at this circuit and distance. Has the benefit of a good draw and should be fitter so can go one better. WEE GEORGIE WOOD (8) has been competitive of late and kept the ball rolling last time when fourth. Won here four back and hasn't missed the top-four since. Player with even luck from the inside of the second row. ALL ABOUT SADIE (3) draws well and added to a string of placings when she came from the back line for third here last time out. Tricky draw for I GOTTA GO (10) but he has been about the mark of late and must be respected.",
